code: /**  * Note: Broadcast mode could be handled directly for all the output channels  * in record writer, so it is no need to select channels via this method.  */ @Override public int selectChannel(SerializationDelegate<StreamRecord<T>> record) {     throw new UnsupportedOperationException("Broadcast partitioner does not support select channels."). }
